name: Milk I
description: I took this photo in Kimolos. It's a very small island close to Milos, but it has the most beautiful beach I've had the opportunity to see in Greece so far. It's also a very calm and authentic island. The milkyway was clearly visible every night after 10Pm, from our bear eyes. It draws in the sky of Kimolos like a map of stars guiding you back home from a long evening out, drinking, eating and watching movies at the open air theaters downtown.
